text: László Cseresnyés (born 30 July 1958) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Veszprém County
